Fetch some JSON from Noko.

For example, fetch some entries like so:

    entries = self.fetch_json(
        'entries',
        query_params={
            'search[from]': '2015-01-01',
            'search[to]': '2015-01-31',
            'search[projects]': [1423, 24545, ]),
        }
    )
